1. Ona koristi *mobilni* telefon da bi se dopala mladiću. (She uses a mobile phone to impress the guy.)

2. *Mobilni* internet je postao nezaobilazan u savremenom svetu. (Mobile internet has become unavoidable in the modern world.)

3. Ovaj *mobilni* uređaj ima mnogo prednosti u odnosu na druge. (This mobile device has many advantages over others.)

4. Ona je prešla na *mobilni* broj, što je korisno za njene poslovne potrebe. (She switched to a mobile number, which is useful for her business needs.)

5. On je kupio *mobilni* telefon koji je izuzetno moderni. (He bought a mobile phone which is extremely modern.)